<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4006928>
    dc:description "Figure 7. Gubernatoriana triangulus sp. nov., holotype male (ZSI, WRC-C.1134). (A) Anterior thoracic sternites; (B) abdomen; (C) left cheliped; (D) left third maxilliped; (E) dorsal view of right G1; (F) ventral view of right G1; (G) dorsal view of terminal article of right G1; (H) right G2. Scale bars: 5 mm (A, B); 10 mm (C); 2.5 mm (D) and 1 mm (E–H)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4006928/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

